<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤١ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَحَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2540">‌سَلَمَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1904">‌ذَرٍّ </a>فِي هَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ الَّذِي ذَكَرَ الْحَكَمُ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قَالَ عُمَرُ: <span class="c2">«بَلْ نُوَلِّيكَ مَا تَوَلَّيْتَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>